values: A dagger is deceptively simple - just a blade and a grip. But the balance must be perfect for quick, precise strikes.
A simple round shield - iron face with oak backing. Protects and strikes in equal measure.
Advanced refinery with better efficiency and heat control.
Balanced steel longsword. The blade flows like water, strikes like thunder.
Basic alchemy table with mortar, pestle, and glassware.
Basic axe for woodcutting. Simple but essential for any aspiring adventurer.
Basic leather protection. Better than nothing, lighter than metal.
Basic refinery for turning raw ores into usable ingots. Essential for any metalworker.
Basic stone forge suitable for working copper and iron. The foundation of smithing.
Basic workbench for assembling mechanical devices.
Binding a fire crystal to ironwood creates a conduit for elemental power. The wood never burns, the crystal never dims - a perfect symbiosis.
Crafting a composite bow requires laminating different materials - wood for flexibility, sinew for power, silk for the string. Patience yields deadly accuracy.
Crafting a warhammer is about managing weight distribution. The crushing head must be perfectly balanced on the shaft, or it becomes a liability rather than a weapon.
Curved steel blade perfect for harvesting delicate plants. Clean cuts preserve quality and maximize yield.
Ethereal mithril axe that phases through wood fibers. Cuts with minimal resistance.
Flexible bamboo rod with silk line and bronze hook. Patience and the right tool can pull dinner from any water.
Forging a steel battleaxe requires balance - too heavy and it's unwieldy, too light and it lacks impact. This versatile weapon can devastate with two hands or still threaten with one.
Improved forge with better heat retention. Can work steel reliably.
Iron amulet holding a water crystal. Feels cool against your skin.
Iron plates protect vital organs. Heavy but reliable.
Legendary mithril pickaxe that sings through stone. Impossibly light yet incredibly effective.
Master forge with crystal enhancement. Can reach extreme temperatures.
Mithril dagger that seems to shimmer out of existence. Wickedly sharp, impossibly light.
Razor-edged steel axe. Ancient trees fall before it.
Reinforced leather boots with iron caps. Protects your feet without slowing you down.
Reinforced leather gloves with iron studs across the knuckles. Your hands are your tools - protect them properly.
Simple copper band with fire crystal. Radiates gentle warmth.
Simple pine bow strung with treated sinew. Not powerful, but reliable.
Simple spear with copper tip. Keep your enemies at a distance.
Solid iron axe for serious forestry work. Bites deep and true.
Steel bracelet with lightning shard. Crackles with stored static.
Steel helm with full face protection. Your head stays attached, which is nice.
Steel pickaxe with perfect balance. Makes hard rock feel like clay.
Steel plate leggings with articulated joints. Protecting your legs without sacrificing mobility is the mark of quality armor.
The foundational smithing technique - blade, tang, handle. Simple in concept, demanding in execution. Every smith remembers their first sword.
Upgraded pickaxe that can tackle tougher deposits. Iron reliability meets practical design.
Your first pickaxe. The gateway to greater resources and deeper discoveries.
Air crystal creates speed foundation. Lightning shard adds electric quickness. Spectral thread binds temporal acceleration. Move like lightning.
Air crystals create fluid motion essence. Spectral thread lightens body, quickens reflexes. Slime gel binds to living form. World seems to slow.
Air crystals deny gravity. Spectral thread lightens physical form. Void essence completes separation from earth. Living ichor binds to body. You float.
Automated collector - iron houses mechanism, light gem identifies targets, spectral thread extends reach, slime gel provides adhesive grip. Saves countless trips.
Basic arrow turret - iron frame for stability, oak mechanism for firing, beetle carapace provides spring tension. Point away from face.
Bear trap - steel forms jaw mechanism, dire fangs form serrated edges. Once closed, nothing escapes. Perfect spring tension required.
Calcining limestone. Creates reactive quicklime - foundation of many processes.
Cluster bomb - steel casing fragments, blast powder creates multiple charges, air crystals ensure wide dispersal. Maximum coverage.
Copper dissolves first into base form. Fire crystal catalyzes transformation to tin. Foundation of alchemical wealth.
Creating bronze. Copper in core determines base, tin in surrounding modifies to alloy - classic 3:1 ratio creates stronger alloy. T1 allows 1 core + 2 surrounding.
Crystal quartz creates magical base, pure potential. Light gems infuse arcane energy. Water crystals stabilize volatile magic into drinkable form. Mana floods back.
Dire fangs dissolve first, releasing strength essence. Fire crystals amplify power. Beetle carapace adds durability to effect. Too early blocks absorption, too late makes it brief.
Dire fangs release primal fury. Fire crystals ignite rage. Storm heart adds raw power. Living ichor binds controlled chaos. Unleash inner beast.
Dire fangs release venom. Shadow core amplifies toxicity. Slime gel stabilizes for storage. Coat weapons with deadly brew.
EMP device - orichalcum frame channels energy, lightning shards provide pulse, storm heart amplifies. Technology's nightmare.
Essence blood provides foundation. Light gem illuminates and purifies. Living ichor amplifies. Miss a peak, lose potency - catch them all, wounds close rapidly.
Fire arrow turret - steel frame withstands heat, birch mechanism fires, fire crystals ignite projectiles. Warm touch to home defense.
Fire bomb - steel casing survives blast, blast powder creates explosion, fire crystals add burning. Melts stone.
Fire crystals generate inner warmth. Phoenix ash adds perpetual heat never fading. Slime gel spreads throughout body. Cold cannot touch you.
Fire then water - must balance before adding earth. Air completes cycle. Balance in bottle - all elements recognize you as kin.
Firing clay to brick. Soft earth becomes hard construction material.
Flamethrower turret - steel frame withstands heat, fire crystals fuel inferno, phoenix ash ensures perpetual burn. Excellent crowd control.
Forging steel from carbon-rich ore. Requires intense heat - cylinders resist then yield.
Forging steel with frost. Perpetually cold metal - crystallizing impossible cold.
Frost mine - iron casing protects mechanism, blast powder triggers, frost essence provides freezing blast. Bury and wait.

Gold base for perfection. Dragon scale adds ancient power. Essence blood provides life. Void essence enables transmutation. Phoenix ash grants rebirth. Storm heart completes opus. Magnum achievement of alchemy.
Golem core provides titan strength. Storm heart adds raw power. Phoenix ash ensures perpetual effect. Essence blood binds all. You feel unstoppable.
Grappling hook - iron forms hook, spectral thread creates unbreakable line, air crystals enable vertical mobility. Hooks distant surfaces.
Healing beacon - steel frame supports, light gems project aura, living ichor provides life force, water crystals extend radius. Continuous healing.
Infusing copper with storm. Perfect conductivity - arcs jump between shards and metal.
Infusing steel with fire. Metal burns without consumption - crystals seep energy in.
Iron dissolves to potential. Coal provides carbon. Fire crystal bonds them into steel. Alchemy surpasses forging.
Iron scales dissolve into liquid stone base. Earth crystal adds flexible protection. Golem core solidifies without rigidity. Skin hardens like metal.
Jetpack for brief flight - mithril frame lightweight, fire crystals provide thrust, air crystals stabilize, phoenix ash ensures sustained burn. Fuel not included.
Laser turret - mithril frame reflects energy, light gems provide power, crystal quartz lenses focus to cutting intensity. Precise and devastating.
Light gems infuse eyes with illumination. Shadow core teaches seeing through darkness. Living ichor carries to vision. Darkness becomes irrelevant.
Lightning cannon - mithril frame conducts perfectly, ironwood mechanism directs, lightning shards provide power, storm heart amplifies. Extremely effective, extremely dangerous.
Limestone dissolves, creating crystalline matrix. Phoenix ash ignites transformation. Chaos becomes order - heat solidifies into stable crystal.
Limestone grinds to powder. Light gem infuses protective shimmer. Slime gel binds into paste. Sheen turns blades.
Living ichor creates sustained healing potential. Light gems infuse persistent illumination. Essence blood binds regenerative effect. Body remembers how to heal continuously.
Living ichor provides life force base. Water crystals amplify properties. Slime gel completes stabilization. Each stage must settle before next.
Living ichor provides raw life force. Light gems purify and concentrate. Pure essence emerges - no impurities, pure vitality.
Living ichor purges toxins from blood. Light gem illuminates and neutralizes poison. Simple but effective - corruption burns away.
Melting sand to glass. Extreme heat transforms granules to clarity.
Milling ash logs. Dense wood, clean grain - satisfying precision.
Milling legendary ironwood. Dense as metal - cylinders strain against it.
Net launcher - iron frame launches, spectral thread forms unbreakable net, beetle carapace weights edges. Reduces movement dramatically.
Poison gas trap - iron casing contains, slime gel creates gas, shadow cores amplify toxicity. Choking clouds on trigger.
Processing birch. White wood with subtle grain - reveals silver interior.
Processing coal to charcoal. Burns hotter, cleaner - essential for advanced work.
Processing maple logs. Light colored wood with fine grain - quality timber.
Processing pine logs. Soft wood cuts easily - resinous scent fills air.
Processing rare ebony. Black as night, hard as steel - exceptional quality.
Proximity alarm - iron housing protects, light gem detects movement, beetle carapace creates sound. Simple but effective early warning.
Refining ancient metal. Channels physical and magical forces - harmonic resonance.
Refining common copper to uncommon. Four compress into one - structure perfects.
Refining common iron to uncommon. Patient work and precise heat.
Refining common steel to uncommon. Carbon bonds align perfectly.
Refining epic adamantine to legendary. Hardness beyond measurement.
Refining epic copper to legendary. Perfect molecular alignment achieved.
Refining epic iron to legendary. Ultimate iron - theoretically perfect.
Refining epic mithril to legendary. Defies physics completely.
Refining epic orichalcum to legendary. Ancient metal awakens fully.
Refining epic platinum to legendary. Ultimate precious metal perfection.
Refining epic steel to legendary. Perfect steel - master smiths weep.
Refining legendary etherion to mythical. Temporal boundaries dissolve.
Refining legendary mithril to mythical. Metal sings in harmonic perfection.
Refining legendary mithril. Metal purifies itself - cylinders align eagerly.
Refining legendary orichalcum to mythical. Complete awakening achieved.
Refining multidimensional metal. Reality bends - impossible configurations work.
Refining platinum ore. Dense white metal - rarer than gold, harder than steel.
Refining rare adamantine to epic. Nearly indestructible becomes truly eternal.
Refining rare bronze to epic. Surpassing legendary smiths of old.
Refining rare copper to epic. Approaching theoretical perfection.
Refining rare iron to epic. Bonds align with supernatural precision.
Refining rare mithril to epic. Weightless perfection approaches.
Refining rare silver to epic. Magical conductivity maximizes.
Refining rare steel to epic. Edge retention becomes legendary.
Refining rare tin to epic. Perfect magical conductivity achieved.
Refining silver ore. Gleaming white metal - resonates with unseen forces.
Refining tin ore. Essential for alloys - cylinders click with different tone than iron.
Refining uncommon bronze to rare. Ancient alloy perfected.
Refining uncommon copper to rare. Grain becomes perfect - impurities purged.
Refining uncommon gold to rare. Lustrous perfection achieved.
Refining uncommon iron to rare. Crystalline structure perfecting.
Refining uncommon steel to rare. Metal sings as imperfections vanish.
Refining uncommon tin to rare. Silvery sheen becomes mirror-bright.
Repair drone - mithril frame enables flight, light gem powers systems, spectral thread manipulates tools, living ichor enables restoration. Fixes what breaks.
Sawing oak into planks. Basic carpentry - blade sings as grain splits clean.
Scanner detecting resources - steel houses sensors, light gems power scanning, crystal quartz focuses detection, air crystals enable remote sensing. Knowledge is power.
Shadow cores create concealment base. Spectral thread bends light around you. Void essence completes erasure. Living ichor binds to living form. You become absence.
Shield generator creating barrier - steel supports projectors, light gems power field, crystal quartz shapes barrier, water crystals distribute energy. Damage breaks on barrier.
Simple explosive - iron casing contains, blast powder explodes. Universal problem solver.
Slime gel creates base. Fire crystal adds warming confidence. Simple but effective - fear melts away.
Slime gel creates slick base. Spectral thread adds supernatural efficiency. Water crystal prevents evaporation. Productivity soars.
Slime gel dissolves first, creating restorative base. Wolf pelt binds mixture second. Watch for gentle green glow - too quick and they won't merge.
Slow field generator - iron anchors reality, frost essence creates temporal drag, crystal projects field, water stabilizes. Everything moves through frozen honey.
Smelting adamantine. Extreme heat required - cylinders groan under strain.
Smelting gold ore. Soft lustrous metal - eternal and untarnishing.
Smelting iron ore. Backbone of civilization - each cylinder reveals metal within stone.
